### GENERAL

# Auth
AUTH_SECRET=""

# DB
# Neon connection string. Used by the app at runtime (neon-http driver) and by
# migrations (node-pg-migrate over node-postgres, run with --no-lock so the pooled
# PgBouncer endpoint is fine — transactions work; only the session advisory lock,
# which we don't need for manual single-operator migrations, is skipped).
DATABASE_URL=""

# Shared secret for the daily Partyflock agenda cron route. Vercel Cron sends it
# as `Authorization: Bearer <CRON_SECRET>`; the route rejects requests without it.
CRON_SECRET=""

### INTEGRATIONS

# Last.fm
LASTFM_KEY=""

# Spotify
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=""
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=""
